parameters: \n<Bath Lady>Go ahead and get your clothes off in a dressing room,\. you silly~

\n<Bath Lady>Good!\.\. I'll gladly clean all the fur you're shedding after you're done~

\n<Bath Lady>Let's make it 15 \G!\.\. You know...\.\.\. I'll have to clean the fur after your bath...
\n<Bath Lady>Go ahead and undress yourself in one of the dressing rooms.
\n<Bath Lady>You'll find your clothes in there after you're done.\.\. I'd usually iron and hang them,\. but...\.\.\. I'm sure you understand~
\n<Bath Lady>Boohoo~\.\. Come back when you have \G to spend cleaning yourself~
"Rules for the hosts of End City's Bathouse"
"1.\.\. No dress or shoes allowed inside the bathing area."
"2.\.\. Obscene acts in the bath are strictly forbidden!"
"3.\.\. Water is a gift of the Spring Goddess.\.\. Waste it and you'll be damned."
